  lines:
  - speakerName: Customer5
    text: )Ahahaha. They got me good, the buzzy bastards. But I fooled em. I fooled
      em all. I got that sweet sweet nectar, They can't have it no more. It's all
      mine now. But I ain't been feelin so good. I guess they got one over on my
      way out.
